valvoline inc vvv company profile  reuterscom x edition united states africa américa latina عربي argentina brasil canada  deutschland españa france india italia  méxico россия united kingdom united states profile valvoline inc vvv related topics stocksstock screenerbasic materialscommodity chemicals overview news key developments people charts financials analysts research pulse vvv on new york consolidated usd  jul  change  chg  9 prev close  open  days high  days low  volume 9 avg vol  wk high  wk low  full description valvoline inc valvoline incorporated on may   is engaged in the production and distribution of automotive commercial and industrial lubricants and automotive chemicals the company operates through three segments core north america quick lubes and international the companys products include all climate durablend and maxlife in addition to the valvolinebranded passenger car motor oils and other automotive lubricant products valvoline provides a range of lubricants used in heavy duty equipment as well as automotive chemicals and fluids its lubricants product category includes product lines such as passenger carlight duty and heavy duty its heavy duty product line includes lubricating solutions for a range of heavy duty applications ranging from onroad to offroad construction mining and power generation equipment its antifreeze product category includes antifreezecoolants for original equipment manufacturers oemsthe companys chemicals product category includes product lines such as maintenance chemicals and coatings its maintenance chemicals product line includes functional and maintenance chemicals ranging from brake fluids and power steering fluids to chemicals designed to clean and maintain optimal performance of fuel cooling and drive train systems its coatings product line includes coatings designed to target rust prevention sound absorption and release agents for automotive and industrial applications its filters product category includes oil and air filters for lightduty vehicles it also offers windshield wiper blades light bulbs serpentine belts and drain plugs in addition to valvolines branded offerings valvoline sells privatelabel products to oems lubricant marketers and aftermarket retailers valvolines private label products include lubricants coolants and chemicalscore north americathe core north america segment sells valvoline and other branded and private label products in the united states and canada to both consumers performing their own automotive maintenance referred to as doityourself diy consumers as well as to installer customers using valvoline products to service vehicles owned by doitforme difm consumers the company sells to its diy consumers through retail auto parts stores such as autozone oreilly auto parts and advance auto parts as well as mass merchandisers and independent auto part stores valvoline also sells various products and services to installer customers such as car dealers general repair shops and various thirdparty quick lube locations directly through distributors valvoline also sells branded products and solutions to heavy duty customers such as onhighway fleets and construction companiesquick lubesthe companys quick lubes segment services the passenger car and light truck quick lube market through platforms including valvolines companyowned franchised valvoline instant oil change vioc stores a retail quick lube service chain by number of stores and express care a quick lube customer platform developed for independent operators purchasing valvoline motor oil and other products pursuant to contracts while displaying valvoline branded signage as of september   the vioc network consisted of  companyowned and  franchised centers and operated in  states the express care platform supports smaller single store operators that do not fit valvolines franchised model and offer other nonquick lube services such as auto repairs and car washes as of september   there were  express care locationsinternationalthe companys international segment sold valvoline and other branded products through its affiliates joint ventures licensees and independent distributors in approximately  countries outside of the united states and canada as of september   its international markets include china india europe the middle east and africa emea latin america and australia pacific its international sales include both passenger car products and heavy duty products used in a range of heavy duty equipment its passenger car motorcycle and light duty truck products are sold internationally through distributors in difm sales channels to installer customers its heavy duty products are sold either directly to customers or through distributorsthe company competes with shell bp exxon mobil grease monkey express oil change superlube american lube fast sinopec and indian oil » full overview of vvv company address valvoline inc  valvoline waylexington   ky   9 p 99 company web links home page officers  directors » more officers  directors valvoline inc news briefmonro muffler brake says on june  its unit signed three year supply agreement with valvoline jul   briefvalvoline says shareholders approve proposed corporate governance enhancements apr   briefvalvoline reports q earnings per share  apr   » more vvv news related topics stocksstock screenerbasic materialscommodity chemicals microsoft personalized ad preferences to opt out of personalized ads in this browser your browser history must allow firstparty and thirdparty cookies and you must have your browsing experience set to not delete browsing history on exit instructions for enabling cookies and configuring your browsing history may be available in your browsers settings privacy or help documentation sign in hold on… we’re sorry but this didn’t work you can’t turn off personalized ads right now because your browser is currently blocking thirdparty cookies we can help you fix this issue let’s get started depending on what brow